Christman, Respondent, v. Thatcher, Overseer, Appellant. (Supreme Court, General Term, Third Department. September 21, 1889.)

Argued before Learned, P. J., and Landon and Putnam, JJ.

No opinion. Order reversed, with $10 costs and printing disbursements. For former reports, see 1 N. Y. Supp. 451; 4 N. Y. Supp. 957.
